---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="MNL Innovation - Managed IT Services"
	keywords=" Managed IT Services, IT Support, IT Solutions, IT Consulting, IT Management"
	description=" MNL Innovation - Managed IT Services"
>
	<div class="bg-white mt-20">
		<main
			class="mx-auto px-4 pb-24 pt-14 sm:px-6 sm:pb-32 sm:pt-16 lg:max-w-7xl lg:px-8"
		>
			<!-- Product -->
			<div
				class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-7 lg:grid-rows-1 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-10 xl:gap-x-16"
			>
				<!-- Product image -->
				<div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:row-end-1">
					<div
						class="aspect-h-3 aspect-w-4 overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-gray-100"
					>
						<img
							src="/images/services/managedIT.webp"
							alt="Managed IT Services"
							class="object-cover object-center bg-repeat"
						/>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Product details -->
				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-2xl sm:mt-16 lg:col-span-3 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-end-2 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div class="flex flex-col-reverse">
						<div class="mt-4">
							<h1
								class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-3xl"
							>
								Managed IT Services
							</h1>

							<h2 id="information-heading" class="sr-only">
								Managed IT Services
							</h2>
						</div>
					</div>

					<p class="mt-6 text-gray-500">
						Managed IT Services involve outsourcing your organization’s IT
						operations to a dedicated provider. Instead of hiring and managing
						an in-house team, you gain access to experienced IT professionals
						who proactively monitor, maintain, and support your technology
						infrastructure. This helps improve efficiency, reduce downtime, and
						ensure your systems stay secure and up to date.
					</p>

					<div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-4 sm:grid-cols-1">
						<a
							href="/contact?service=managed"
							class="flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-md border bg-[#00629E] px-8 py-3 text-base font-medium text-white hover:bg-[#00629E] hover:text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2"
						>
							Contact
						</a>
					</div>

					<!-- Lista de servicios -->
					<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
						<h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-900">
							Key Features of Our Managed IT Services
						</h3>
						<div class="prose prose-sm mt-4 text-gray-500">
							<ul role="list" class="space-y-6">
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>24/7 Monitoring & Support:</strong> Continuous oversight
											of your systems to detect and resolve issues before they affect
											your business.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Proactive Maintenance:</strong> Regular updates, patches,
											and system optimization to keep everything running smoothly.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Data Backup & Disaster Recovery:</strong> Automated
											backups and tested recovery plans to protect your data.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex w-6 justify-center -bottom-6"
									>
										<div class="w-px bg-gray-200"></div>
									</div>
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Cybersecurity Protection:</strong> Threat detection,
											antivirus, firewalls, and user awareness to safeguard your
											business.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Cloud & On-Premise Support:</strong> We manage both
											local infrastructure and cloud services.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
								<li class="relative flex gap-x-4">
									<div
										class="relative flex h-6 w-6 flex-none items-center justify-center bg-white"
									>
										<div
											class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-gray-100 ring-1 ring-[#1dc690]"
										>
										</div>
									</div>
									<p class="flex-auto py-0.5 text-xs leading-5 text-gray-500">
										<span class="font-medium text-gray-900"
											><strong>Scalable Solutions:</strong> Services tailored to
											fit your business growth and evolving needs.</span
										>
									</p>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
				>
					<div>
						<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
							<h3
								class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-800 text-xl font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#1dc690] py-6"
							>
								What’s included in Our Managed IT Services
							</h3>
						</div>

						<div
							id="tab-panel-faq"
							class="text-sm text-gray-500"
							aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
							role="tabpanel"
							tabindex="0"
						>
							<h3 class="sr-only">
								What’s Included in Our Managed IT Services
							</h3>

							<dl>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Network monitoring and infrastructure management
								</dt>

								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									User helpdesk and technical support
								</dt>

								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Microsoft 365 and Google Workspace management
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Endpoint protection and patch management
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Cloud migration and management
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Hardware and software procurement consulting
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									IT policy development and compliance support
								</dt>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									Regular performance reporting and audits
								</dt>
							</dl>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
						<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
							<h3
								class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-800 text-xl font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#1dc690] py-6"
							>
								Technologies & Platforms We Support
							</h3>
						</div>

						<div
							id="tab-panel-faq"
							class="text-sm text-gray-500"
							aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
							role="tabpanel"
							tabindex="0"
						>
							<h3 class="sr-only">Technologies & Platforms We Support</h3>

							<dl>
								<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
									<strong>Microsoft 365:</strong> Full administration and support,
									including Exchange, Teams, SharePoint, and Intune.
								</dt>
							</dl>

							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Azure & AWS:</strong> Cloud infrastructure setup, migration,
								and ongoing management.
							</dt>

							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Endpoint Management Tools:</strong> Microsoft Intune, RMM
								platforms (like NinjaOne, Atera).
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Security Solutions:</strong> Bitdefender, SentinelOne, Cisco
								Umbrella, multi-factor authentication (MFA).
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Backup & Recovery:</strong> Veeam, Acronis, Datto.
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong>Collaboration Tools:</strong> Microsoft Teams, Zoom, Slack,
								and more.
							</dt>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								<strong> Remote Monitoring & Management (RMM):</strong> Real-time
								analytics and automation to support your environment efficiently.
							</dt>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div
				class="mx-auto mt-16 w-full max-w-2xl lg:col-span-4 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none"
			>
				<div class="mt-10 border-t border-gray-200 pt-10">
					<div class="border-b border-gray-200">
						<h3
							class="text-gray-700 hover:text-gray-800 text-xl font-medium border-b-2 border-transparent hover:border-[#1dc690] py-6"
						>
							Frequently Asked Questions
						</h3>
					</div>

					<div
						id="tab-panel-faq"
						class="text-sm text-gray-500"
						aria-labelledby="tab-faq"
						role="tabpanel"
						tabindex="0"
					>
						<h3 class="sr-only">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>

						<dl>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q1: What is included in your Managed IT Services plan? 365?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Our plans cover 24/7 system monitoring, helpdesk support,
									patch management, backup and recovery, cybersecurity
									solutions, cloud services, and more. We tailor each plan to
									your specific needs.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q2: Do you support remote and hybrid teams?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Yes. We support fully remote, hybrid, and in-office
									environments, ensuring secure access, collaboration tools, and
									device management for all employees.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q3: How do Managed IT Services help reduce costs?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: You eliminate the need for a full-time internal IT
									department while gaining access to a team of certified
									experts. You also avoid costly downtime, security breaches,
									and inefficient systems.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q4: Is my data secure with your service?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: Absolutely. We implement industry best practices for
									cybersecurity, encryption, multi-layered protection, and
									regular vulnerability assessments.
								</p>
							</dd>
							<dt class="mt-10 font-medium text-gray-900">
								Q5: Can you manage our existing IT infrastructure or do we need
								to switch everything?
							</dt>
							<dd class="prose prose-sm mt-2 max-w-none text-gray-500">
								<p>
									A: We can work with your current infrastructure and gradually
									improve it over time. We do not require you to start from
									scratch unless major upgrades are needed.
								</p>
							</dd>
						</dl>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
</Layout>
